      <outline text="Victor Bericoto (San Francisco, California) — Left oblique strain, exited a game on July 9 (2026-07-10)" type="link" url="https://www.mlb.com/news/giants-injuries-and-roster-moves" description="Giants lose another outfield option amid multiple oblique injuries in the unit"/>
