      <outline text="Endy Rodriguez (Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania) — Left glute strain (2026-07-08)" type="link" url="https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2026/07/pirates-to-place-endy-rodriguez-on-injured-list.html" description="Pirates lose their starting catcher for at least 10 days"/>
